Support legal aspects of transport sector governance reforms, including compliance, enforcement, and institutional mandates;
Coordinate with ECOWAS institutions, national authorities, legal experts, and development partners;
Deliver workshops, consultations, and capacity-building activities related to transport legal frameworks and regulatory reforms;
Contribute to monitoring, reporting, and technical reviews related to legal reform activities.




